<p>Because this event procedure comes into effect directly upon reception of a new order, the status of the main order is not taken into consideration. Thus, delivery orders will also be created for main orders that are in status <strong>3.0</strong> (or <strong>1.0</strong> if you work with auction platforms such as eBay) and will adopt the status of the main order.</p>
