<div class="title">Generating a return slip automatically</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Set up an event procedure that automatically generates return slips. If you select the event <strong>New return (by customer)</strong> and the filter <strong>Client (store)</strong>, blank return slips are generated with each incoming return and only have to be provided for downloading.</p>
</div>
</td>
</tr>
