<div class="title">Tip: Changing values</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>You can recognise changeable values by a drop-down list or by the appearing <strong>pencil</strong> icon. Click on the pencil icon to edit the required parameters (e.g. image 16, the <strong>Weight</strong> entry in the top left corner).</p>
</div>
</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
</div>
